name: Opee Sea Killer
Lore: 'The opee sea killer catches its prey with a long, flexible tongue. It uses camouflage to assist in hunting prey, as well as avoiding larger predators like the sando aqua monster.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Cancels Sando Aqua Monster. While no card here, may place an opponent''s just-drawn battle destiny face-up here. If opponent just drew battle destiny with the same card title as card here, place both cards in opponent''s Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
